author: thorsten
msg: LABS-139 Added delay between http requests.
Now you can define the milliseconds of delay between http request. You have now three different implementations for the interface DelayTimer.
Only applies a fixed delay to the request. Set the property delay in the spring context.
Generate a random delay between 0ms and the value specified. Set the property delay in the spring context.
Generate a random delay and combine with a fixed delay. Set the property delay and fixedDelay in the spring context.
Feature submitted by Javier Puerto. Muchas gracias, monstro.
